   <title>NMC B3 Operational Model 47 by 51 Northern Hemisphere Tropospheric Analyses, daily 1959-1972</title>
   <summary>
      <p>This dataset contains daily gridded Northern Hemisphere
              analyses from NMC's operational model on a 47 by 51
              polar-stereographic grid centered on the North Pole.  Available
              parameters include geopotential height, temperature, stream
              functions, thickness, and vertical velocity for various levels
              and layers through the troposphere.  In general, the grids
              cover the period from January 1959 to December 1972, but periods
              for individual parameters will vary.</p>
   </summary>
